Devin Dimmitt attempts a lift at the AAU Power Lifting World International Championships in Las Vegas on Sept. 25. (Courtesy photo) Posted: Wednesday, October 21, 2015 8:02 pm | Updated: 8:14 pm, Wed Oct 21, 2015. Devin Dimmitt breaks his own power lifting record By DEREK NOEHREN dnoehren@nptelegraph.com nptelegraph.com 
Devin Dimmitt has done it again. 
The 21-year-old from North Platte broke his own state, national and world record by bench pressing 413.36 pounds at the AAU Power Lifting World International Championships in Las Vegas on Sept. 25.   Need an account? Create one now. Subscription required
